"title": "5478: property, houses",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5478",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>From at least the time of the flood people have built houses to live in and these have been a major part of their property; the temple was seen as God's house.</p>\n<h2>Houses are a major part of people's property</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:22\">EXO 12:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:4\">HAG 1:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:3\">HEB 3:3</a></p>\n<h2>The homeless have no property</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:11\">1CO 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:8\">JOB 24:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:5\">LAM 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:58\">LUK 9:58</a></p>\n<h2>Property has no lasting value</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:34\">HEB 10:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:11-Deut6:12\">DEU 6:11–6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a></p>\n<h2>Materials used in house building</h2>\n<h3>Clay</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:19\">JOB 4:19</a></p>\n<h3>Brick</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:11-Exod1:14\">EXO 1:11–1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:10\">ISA 9:10</a></p>\n<h3>Stone and wood</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:40\">LEV 14:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:42\">LEV 14:42</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:11\">HAB 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>Luxurious building materials</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:39\">1KI 22:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:6\">EST 1:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:15\">AMO 3:15</a></p>\n<h2>Houses are protected by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:1\">PSA 127:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:27\">EXO 12:27</a></p>\n<h2>Houses as dwellings</h2>\n<h3>For sinners</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:1\">JOS 2:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:27\">PRO 7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:9\">PRO 21:9</a></p>\n<h3>For friends</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:6\">ZEC 13:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:38\">LUK 10:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:1-John12:2\">JHN 12:1–12:2</a></p>\n<h2>Other uses for houses</h2>\n<h3>For work</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:2\">JER 18:2</a></p>\n<h3>For hospitality</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:5-Luke10:7\">LUK 10:5–10:7</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:11\">MAT 10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:10\">MRK 6:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:3\">GEN 19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:35\">MAT 25:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:15\">ACT 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:10\">1TI 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:2\">HEB 13:2</a></p>\n<h3>For church gatherings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:20\">ACT 20:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:5\">ROM 16:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:19\">1CO 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:15\">COL 4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:2\">PHM 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>As palaces</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:2\">2SA 7:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:1-1Kgs7:2\">1KI 7:1–7:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:39\">1KI 22:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:29-Dan4:30\">DAN 4:29–4:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:8\">MAT 11:8</a></p>\n<h2>Legislation concerning houses</h2>\n<h3>Respecting the houses of others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:17\">EXO 20:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:2\">MIC 2:2</a></p>\n<h3>Redemption of property</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:29-Lev25:33\">LEV 25:29–25:33</a></p>\n<h2>The LORD's house</h2>\n<h3>God's promise to David</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:11\">2SA 7:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:5\">1KI 5:5</a></p>\n<h3>Solomon's building</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:1\">1KI 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:2\">1KI 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:7\">1KI 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:12\">1KI 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:14\">1KI 6:14</a></p>\n<h3>Ezra's rebuilding</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:9-Ezra3:10\">EZR 3:9–3:10</a></p>\n<h3>It was a place to meet God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:6\">PSA 23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4\">PSA 27:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:10\">PSA 84:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps122:1\">PSA 122:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:7\">ISA 56:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:18\">JOL 3:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:16-John2:17\">JHN 2:16–2:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:9\">PSA 69:9</a></p>\n<h3>It is a picture of the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19-Eph2:20\">EPH 2:19–2:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:9-1Cor3:11\">1CO 3:9–3:11</a></p>",
